init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You watch this new life unfold.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Why are you watching this new life?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see your past selves, all watching the new life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You wonder if they are going to be reincarnated again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look back at the screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You wonder if you are the only one in this room.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look around the room again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You were all one soul, and you were all here to learn from each other.
